2015 IHSA Football Playoffs - First Round Matchups - WREX.com – Rockford’s News Leader Member Center: 2015 IHSA Football Playoffs - First Round Matchups Posted: dcohen@wrex.com ROCKFORD (WREX) - 
The 256-team, eight-class field for the 2015 IHSA football playoffs was announced Saturday night. Here are all the matchups for Stateline squads in next week's first round to be played on October 30 and October 31. 
Class 1A#9 Forreston (7-2) at #8 Dakota (7-2)#13 Westminster Christian (6-3) at #4 Polo (9-0) 
#12 Warren (6-3) at #5 Hope Academy (8-1) 
#10 Stockton (7-2) at #7 Galena (7-2) 
#14 Princeville (5-4) vs #3 Lena-Winslow (9-0) 
Class 2A#15 Christian Life (5-4) vs #2 Annawan-Wethersfield (8-1) 
Class 3A#9 Lisle (7-2) at #8 Byron (7-2) 
#14 Winnebago (5-4) at #3 IC Catholic (8-1) 
Class 4A#16 Genoa-Kingston at #1 Phillips (9-0) 
#15 Coal City (5-4) at #2 Marengo (9-0) 
#14 Dixon (6-3) at #3 Rockford Lutheran (9-0) 
#11 St. Edward at #6 Richmond-Burton (8-1) 
Class 5A#10 Sycamore (6-3) at #7 Nazareth Academy (7-2)
